# Registry Entry Template

Add this entry to `src/components/registry.ts`.

```typescript
{
  id: '{{ID}}',
  name: '{{NAME}}',
  category: '{{CATEGORY}}',
  path: '@/components/{{ID}}',  // Flat structure: each component has its own folder
  purpose: {
    what: '{{PURPOSE_WHAT}}',
    where: '{{PURPOSE_WHERE}}',
    notFor: '{{PURPOSE_NOT_FOR}}'
  },
  variants: {
    {{#each VARIANTS}}
    {{axis}}: { options: [{{optionsArray}}], default: '{{default}}' },
    {{/each}}
  },
  composition: {
    uses: [{{USES}}],
    usedBy: []
  },
  related: [{{RELATED}}],
  guidelines: '{{GUIDELINES}}'
}
```

## Placeholder Values

| Placeholder | Description | Example |
|-------------|-------------|---------|
| `{{ID}}` | kebab-case identifier | `'summary-card'` |
| `{{NAME}}` | PascalCase component name | `'SummaryCard'` |
| `{{CATEGORY}}` | Component category | `'cards'`, `'ui'`, `'layout'` |
| `{{PURPOSE_WHAT}}` | What it does | `'Display key metrics in a compact format'` |
| `{{PURPOSE_WHERE}}` | Usage contexts | `'Dashboards, overview sections'` |
| `{{PURPOSE_NOT_FOR}}` | What not to use for | `'Detailed data (use DataTable)'` |
| `{{VARIANTS}}` | Variant axis definitions | See below |
| `{{USES}}` | Components this uses | `'Card', 'Icon'` |
| `{{RELATED}}` | Similar components | `'Card', 'KpiLayout'` |
| `{{GUIDELINES}}` | Usage notes | `'Use for 1-3 key metrics'` |

## Variant Format

```typescript
variants: {
  size: { options: ['sm', 'md', 'lg'], default: 'md' },
  variant: { options: ['default', 'highlighted'], default: 'default' }
}
```

## After Adding Entry

1. Update `usedBy` arrays for any components listed in `uses`
2. Verify TypeScript compiles without errors
3. Check ComponentLibrary displays the new entry
